{"tid":993806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥記經理 冷藏庫裡抽插未成年女兼職 圖","createTime":"2019-01-24T08:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T08:50:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"74c27d233b3dfdd31f80eeb3b6639176db9bfd10","tid":993806,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"美國明尼蘇達州一間麥當勞的男經理，被控在店內冷藏庫性侵一名14歲女工讀生，之後一個月內再四度強姦她。據悉，經理自女方入職後便頻頻示好，多給她工作時數，又以現金支付薪資來避開童工法。控方表示，考慮到被告濫用職權和受害者年齡，將要求法庭重判。<br />\n<br />\n案發的麥當勞位於楓林市（Maple Grove），24歲夜班經理艾柏托里奧（Andrew Otero Albertorio）被控5項一級性侵罪，周二首次出庭。據訴訟內容，艾柏托里奧在14歲女員工去年夏天到職後，經常對女方調情，兩人會透過社群平台Snapchat傳訊息，之後艾柏托里奧開始有親密舉動，企圖親吻工讀生，但遭拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n艾柏托里奧曾告訴女方「想和妳做愛」，但女方婉拒，並表示不想他因為和未成年人發生性關係而捲入麻煩。上月初，她在冷藏庫裡時，艾柏托里奧進來找她，將她逼入角落，求歡被拒後就強暴了她。接下來一個月他繼續性侵對方，地點分別是在麥當勞休息室、艾柏托里奧的車內和家中。<br />\n<br />\n受害人表示，艾柏托里奧給她編排額外的工作時數，並自行支薪，藉此規避兒童少年工作法對未成年人的工時限制。本案將於下月22日再開庭，檢察官認為，艾柏托里奧濫用自己權威地位，多次性侵未成年人，若一級性侵指控成立，將要求法官判處長期監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190124/59178248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190124%2F59178248&d=tV9qdyV9zZdslbmYcqdCeKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5e550942\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190124%2F59178248&h=a75fc2a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190124/59178248</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190124/large/1548292180_c239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190124%2Flarge%2F1548292180_c239.jpg&h=b0617972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n似引誘"},{"pid":"3d48a596f349b9aa9666151972a72309738be692","tid":993806,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"接下來一個月他繼續性侵對方，地點分別是在麥當勞休息室、艾柏托里奧的車內和家中。<br />\n<br />\n一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺明勞資糾紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a9badd8bbcb9628dd704985d8ae2e2707733e3","tid":993806,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187d3b9fee9d488455dd3bf682287411b2434f6d","tid":993806,"uid":209225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"14碎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf8c218c11d4c53b9010f1f0178535e1ac617e4","tid":993806,"uid":24044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3d48a596f349b9aa9666151972a72309738be692","tid":993806,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"接下來一個月他繼續性侵對方，地點分別是在麥當勞休息室、艾柏托里奧的車內和家中。<br />\n<br />\n一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺明勞資糾紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"點解姦完一鑊，條女又會去左條仔既屋企同車內？ 勞資..."},{"pid":"76d10afa3ac55128222c0da46444c6170072ea50","tid":993806,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"條撚準備"},{"pid":"cbf35b439a7cf54a8bf34c0079fb2919095c133b","tid":993806,"uid":93938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"條女張圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b4697e8b054eeec8aade875e01d43d746f6fa4","tid":993806,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy